quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  11,82,"flma ja' 'amruna bnzwl aleadhab bihim jaealna eali qrythm alty kanuu yaeishun fiha safilaha fqlbnaha, wa'amtarna ealayhim hijaratan min tin mtsllib mtyn, qad suff bedha 'iilaa bed mttabet, mellamt eind allah belamt maerufat la tshakil hijaratan alard, wama hadhih alhijarat alty amtrha allah ealaa qawm lut min kafaar quraysh bibaeid 'ana yumtaru bmthlha. wafi hdha tahdid likuli eas mtmrrid ealaa allh"
  11,83,"flma ja' 'amruna bnzwl aleadhab bihim jaealna eali qrythm alty kanuu yaeishun fiha safilaha fqlbnaha, wa'amtarna ealayhim hijaratan min tin mtsllib mtyn, qad suff bedha 'iilaa bed mttabet, mellamt eind allah belamt maerufat la tshakil hijaratan alard, wama hadhih alhijarat alty amtrha allah ealaa qawm lut min kafaar quraysh bibaeid 'ana yumtaru bmthlha. wafi hdha tahdid likuli eas mtmrrid ealaa allh"
  11,84,"warslna 'iilaa \"mdyn\" 'akhahum sheybana, fqal: ya qawm aebuduu allah whdh, lays lakum min 'ilh yastahiqu alebadt ghyrh jl wela, fakhlsu lah alebadt, wala tanqusuu alnnas huquqahum fi mkayylhm wmwazynhm, 'iiniy 'arakum fi saeat eysh, wa'iiniy 'akhaf ealaykum -bsbb 'inqas almikyal walmyzan- eadhab yawm yhyt bkm"
  11,85,"waya qawm atmmu almikyal walmizan baledl, wala tunqisu alnaas haqahum fi eumum ashyayhm, wala tsyru fi al'ard taemalun fiha bmeasy allah wanashr alfsad"
  11,86,"'in ma yabqaa lakum baed 'iyfa' alkayl walmizan min alribh alhlal khayr lakum mmma takhudhunah balttfyf wnhwh min alksb alhram, 'iin kuntum tuminun biallah hqa, famtthlu amrh, wama 'ana ealaykum brqyb ahsy ealaykum aemalkm"
  11,87,"qalu: ya shueayb ahdhh alsalat alty tdawm ealayha tamuruk bi'ana natruk ma yebdh abawuna min al'asnam walawthan, 'aw 'an nmtne ean altasaruf fi kasb 'amwaluna bima nastatie min aihtial wmkr? waqaluu -asthza'an bh-: 'iinak la'ant alhalim alrshyd"
  11,88,"qal sheyb: ya qawm 'ara'aytum 'iin kunt ealaa tariq wadih min rabiy fima 'adeukum 'iilayh min 'ikhlas alebadt lh, wfyma 'anhakum eanh min 'ifsad almal, warazaqani minh rzqana waseana halalana tybana? wama 'urid 'an 'ukhalifakum fartkb amrana nhytkm enh, wama 'urid fima amrkm bih wanhakm eanh 'iilaa 'islahkm qadr taqty wasttaety, wama tawfiqi -fy 'iisabat alhaqu wamuhawalat 'islahkm- 'iilaa ballh, ealaa allah wahdah tawakalt wa'iilayh 'arjie baltwbt wal'inabt"